{"tid":1095846,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)肚餓遊戲1-4","createTime":"2019-04-07T10:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T19:29:28.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d9bdfd0d5b07d4bbb576be8815e7569e4fc4fa50","tid":1095846,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:08:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=bZmkWp0iUYBi2b5pBzw%2FEVSbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=1e030ab5\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=bZmkWp0iUYBi2b5pBzw%2FEVSbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=883c472c\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=bZmkWp0iUYBi2b5pBzw%2FEVSbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=e5075cb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/d7/The_Hunger_Games_Mockingjay_-_Part_2_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fd7%2FThe_Hunger_Games_Mockingjay_-_Part_2_Poster.jpg&h=aa40a834&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事內容背景為一個位於北美洲的一個反烏托邦的虛構國家「施惠國」，由史諾總統統治12個行政區。施惠國為了維持恐怖的統治制度以及鎮壓人民，他們有一個作為懲罰過去在第13區的起義及平息社會叛亂，以及用來瓦解地區的方法，每個行政區必須提供兩個「貢品」&mdash; 通過抽籤選定12至18歲的男孩和女孩各一人，投身於年度盛會，每年必須在電視直播的《飢餓遊戲》中競爭，他們必須在一個廣闊舞台上戰鬥至死，唯一倖存者在最後將會獲得名與利..<br />\n<br />\n2.在第74屆飢餓遊戲勝出後，凱妮絲與比德以勝利者的姿態回到第12區的家鄉，二人都獲得豐厚的獎金，從此衣食無憂，凱妮絲原以為生活自此便安定下來，回到家鄉的她卻患上創傷後壓力症。原來她在比賽的最後關頭，迫使國會改變比賽規則的舉措，讓民眾視為反抗國會暴政的代表人物，此舉除了讓國會面目無光外..<br />\n<br />\n3.故事承接上一集，敘述凱妮絲在遊戲中獲救後將與普魯塔克和黑密契對都城展開革命....。<br />\n「燃燒的女孩」凱妮絲艾佛丁在大旬祭上被反抗軍救走，比德卻不幸落入都城手裡。<br />\n凱妮絲被帶到傳說中已成廢墟的第13區，在反抗軍領袖柯茵和戰友支持下，銜命成為革命的象徵，領導施惠國各區叛變，對抗專制又腐敗的都城，同時也心繫比德安危，傾力籌劃營救行動..<br />\n<br />\n4.故事承接上集：迫於情勢，凱妮絲艾佛丁開始領導施惠國的各區叛變，對抗專制又腐敗的都城。隨著這場決定施惠國命運的戰爭愈演愈烈，都城控制下的其他區也趨向毀滅。凱妮絲必須確定她能信任誰及她需要完成的使命，以免她所愛的一切遭受危及..<br />\n<br />\n7 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=bZmkWp0iUYBi2b5pBzw%2FEVSbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=fbd247b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=bZmkWp0iUYBi2b5pBzw%2FEVSbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=4deb3d04\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056f3a2a1c527af0d1ef4d5b1c059f3850724381","tid":1095846,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:08:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223f7024acaa776e7e67c8acd284b1d74dbcf2a6","tid":1095846,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike